                  EU&#39;s general data protection regulation</a>, such as restrictions on the processing of personal
                  data in certain situations. Requests must be sent in writing to the controller. If necessary, the controller may ask
                  the applicant to prove his or her identity. The controller will respond to the customer within the timeframe set out
                  in the EU Data Protection Regulation (generally within one month).</p>
